            "collapse": true,
            "title": "How long will it take to receive my order?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>Since our items are made-to-order, please allow <strong>1-2 business days</strong> for production. Once shipped, delivery time depends on the option you choose: <strong>Standard (3–4 business days)</strong> or <strong>Economy (5–8 business days)</strong>.</p>",
